Student Manager Assignment

 Description
This is a Java program to manage student records.  
It allows adding, viewing, updating, and deleting students, with data saved to a file using serialization.



Features
- Add new students (`ID`, `Name`, `Age`, `Grade`, `Address`)
- View all students
- Update student details by ID
- Delete students by ID
- Data persists in a file (`students.ser`) between program runs


